    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use, such as light stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats remain supportive and supple, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. All electronic systems, including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation, have been tested and are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with all services performed at recommended intervals. It recently received a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a multi-point inspection to ensure it is road-trip ready. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a confident and comfortable driving experience. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, preserving its overall integrity and making it a standout choice in its class.",
      "price": 36500.0,
